Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.00,0:23:49.43,cn.sub,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\c&Hffffff&\4c&H000000&\bord0\shad2}真实{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.01,0:23:48.58,cn.sub,NTP,0,0,0,,好狡猾好狡猾好狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.01,0:23:48.58,jp.sub,NTP,0,0,0,,ずるいずるいずるい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.85,0:23:49.43,cn.sub,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么生气
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.85,0:23:49.43,jp.sub,NTP,0,0,0,,なんで怒るの